1. *Ruke* su mi se ukočile od hladnoće. (My hands froze from the cold.)
2. Spustio je *ruke* u krilo. (He lowered his hands into his lap.)
3. *Ruku* sam podigao u znak zahvalnosti. (I raised my hand as a sign of gratitude.)
4. Trljala je *rukama* oči da bi se probudila. (She rubbed her eyes to wake up.)
5. Obuhvatila me je *rukama* oko struka. (She embraced me with her arms around the waist.)